dcterms:description: A dataset used as a benchmark for evaluating the performance of using MDM models as pre-trained models on the SDM task, containing words and their senses with corresponding usage examples.

dcterms:description: A dataset constructed from WordNet for the MDM-Easy task, where definitions are aligned with their contexts.
dcterms:title: MDM-WordNet

dcterms:description: A dataset created for the MDM-Hard task, which does not require alignment between contexts and definitions.
